Dematic is a supplier of integrated automated supply chain technology, software and services. With a growth rate of 25% in 2016 Dematic is listed as the world's third-largest materials handling systems supplier. The company employs over 6,000 people and has engineering centres and manufacturing facilities in the United States, Mexico, Australia, Germany, Italy and China. Its customer base includes small, medium and large companies.
Since November 2016 Dematic has been a member of KION Group. Dematic's headquarters are located in Grand Rapids, Michigan.
